Do you need to add some fun to your classroom?!⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
I’m telling you, Novel Effect can do that for you! I’m obsessed with this app and so are my students…. Except they don’t know it’s an app! I hide my iPad inside a binder and place it behind me. While I’m reading it follows along and the students think the book is magic ✨ ⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
My kindergarteners are so engaged in the read aloud. I mean, how couldn’t they be?!? Even if you have older students, they will still love it! It even pulls me in while I’m reading and I can’t help but laugh with some of the funny sound effects or character voice too. ⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Teachers and even parents, this is a must try!⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Drop your favorite emoji if you want me to share some of my students reactions while I’m  reading 👇🏼🥰⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣

OH. MY. GOODNESS! ⁣❤️❤️❤️❤️⁣⁣

It’s done. It’s here. I’m so excited!!!⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
On my roadtrip to California I spent hours upon hours creating this new resource. Let me introduce you to the digital iReady incentive chart!!!!⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
This year is my first year doing @myiready and let me tell you… when I started to implement the iReady incentive charts the students loved them! Their focus and drive to do well definitely increased. ⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
If you’re a teacher like me, you would love to do it all but you don’t always have the time, energy, or resources to do it all. Well I’m here to help! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
This digital chart takes the prep time and energy away, but also helps those that don’t have the resources to trace a chart. However, I also have a chart version available to trace for those that like to put them on chart paper. Ekkk! I’m so excited! I have it on my TPT for only $1 for the next 48hours!!! ⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Let me know in the comments what you think and if I should make them for the entire school year 💗⁣⁣

Does your school do an APEX fundraising program?! This is my first year being a classroom teacher at a school that does it and I’m loving it so far! ⁣
⁣
It’s helps our school raise money all while their leaders give PBIS-based leadership lessons for 2 weeks.⁣ At the end we have a FUN RUN! 🏃🏼‍♀️
⁣
We started yesterday and our class won the first contest! The challenge was whose team “class” can get the most sign-ins on their accounts. We got 100% of our class families to sign-in 🎉 We got this huge metal to wear for the day and we also get to pie one of the leaders in the face this Friday. My students are soooo excited!!!⁣
⁣
I would love to hear what fundraisers your school does. We are working really hard to fundraise for a new playground. We need one bad! 😳⁣
⁣
#schoolfundraiser #schoolfundraising #apexfundraiser #pbis #pbischool #funrun #teacher #teacherssupportteachers #teachersofinstagram #teachersofig #elementaryteacher

This digital iReady chart has been a game changer for my kindergarten classroom! ⁣ ⁣ ⁣
⁣
You might be saying game changer? Ummm yea, okay. Sure.⁣ 😒 ⁣ ⁣
⁣
But let me tell you why!⁣ ⁣ ⁣
⁣
1) I have more wall space for other things!⁣ ⁣
2) My students are practicing counting and writing tally marks everyday.⁣ ⁣
3) My students are spending less time trying to write their initials or coloring in the boxes, which means they are getting back to their computers faster to start the next lesson.⁣ ⁣
4) My engagement is even higher because they love watching the digital picture grow with color! ⁣ ⁣ ⁣
⁣
Another great thing for me, personally… the chart is already made and I don’t have to make one next year. So more planning/prep time for me!!! @officaliready ⁣ ⁣ ⁣
⁣
#iready #ireadymath #ireadyreading #anchorcharts #digitalanchorcharts #incentivechartanchorchart #kindergarten #kindergartenteacher #teacher #elementaryteacher #teacherssupportteachers

Just like that we are off to spring break! ⁣⁣⁣

We had so much fun today with our grade level egg hunt challenge! Swipe over to see all the eggs in the field for all 5 of our classes.  Each pair had to find 1 egg that had each letter of A-L on it. Once we got back to class they had to solve the addition and subtraction problems in each egg. They solved it on their recording sheets. They did so good and we did it in style! We always love a good pajama day 💖⁣⁣⁣
